    &lt;/property&gt;
    &lt;property name=&quot;dialect&quot;&gt;
      NHibernate.Dialect.MySQL55InnoDBDialect
    &lt;/property&gt;

See [documentation][1] **Table 3.3. NHibernate SQL Dialects** for possible dialects for MySql.
	Also `Data Source=` in your `connection.connection_string` looks strange to me. I would remove this string.
	
If not done already, you need to install and reference Nuget package MySql.Data in your project.


